{"id": "1197172135668498442", "channel_id": "1197172135668498442", "type": 0, "author_id": "1188482378948165682", "author_name": "phantom_ye", "author_bot": false, "content": "视频里第一回合的超维空间打出砍头后应该是可以击杀第一条命的，但是弥利亚姆在这里重生了回血了没有进去二阶段，这是bug还是什么特殊机制吗？", "timestamp": "2024-01-17T13:34:39.526000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1197172136637366272", "filename": "Screenrecorder-2024-01-17-21-27-27-436.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 14548114, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1197172135668498442/1197172136637366272/Screenrecorder-2024-01-17-21-27-27-436.mp4?ex=6a00896f&is=69ff37ef&hm=cb959a9554ae2af1975ac4f947858128f8b1e5dd0d1ffc8572b04bae16c99a3f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197172135668498442", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」H5-10弥利亚姆bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1197179881310666762", "channel_id": "1197179881310666762", "type": 0, "author_id": "1028237816183922748", "author_name": "suguri2566", "author_bot": false, "content": "打深海无光时发现的，怪物攻击我方导致损失10%最大血量，触发时灵摆『潮涌』的效果，触手攻击导致触发异形之心降低力量的效果，怪物攻击结束后，进入下一回合，降低力量效果消失，但是异形之心每回合6次的限制没能按照回合重置\n\n简单总结：在怪物回合触发异形之心效果，其计数会带入下一回合，导致下一回合无法完整触发异形之心的效果", "timestamp": "2024-01-17T14:05:26.231000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-17T14:18:23.641000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197179881310666762", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」有关造物“异形之心”的触发问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1197210781037629461", "channel_id": "1197210781037629461", "type": 0, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "建議：\n1、顯示玩家在深潛走的格數\n2、在血量旁邊加個百分比（比如100/200［50%］）\n3、出個回歸活動和回歸劇情\nBug：\n1、護盾會繼承到下回合（100%）\n2、超過一定回合（目前是到12回合就會這樣），牌堆會突然多一堆症狀卡（最少4張，最多不知道）", "timestamp": "2024-01-17T16:08:13.300000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-01-17T16:54:11.215000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "31", "emoji_id": "790263726804434945", "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197210781037629461", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "💭「處理中」關於建議和bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480", "1181168158678204497"]}
